# GitHub Language Detection Overrides
# This repository is a Linux kernel research project (C / patches).
# We want to ensure C shows as the primary language.

# Mark Python post-processing tools as documentation/utilities so they don't dominate the language bar.
tools/postprocess/*.py linguist-documentation

# Ensure eBPF scripts are counted as code (often categorized as C-like).
tools/bpftrace/*.bt linguist-language=C

# Markdown and SVG are already ignored by default, but let's be explicit if needed.
docs/*.md linguist-documentation
diagrams/*.svg linguist-documentation
patches/*.patch linguist-documentation
